    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "TO : Director, FBI",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "DATE: September 4, 1947",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "FROM : SAC, Phoenix",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "SUBJECT: REPORTS OF FLYING DISCS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "b7c",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "[REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "ATTENTION: ASSISTANT DIRECTOR D. M. LADD",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Reference is made to San Francisco letter dated August 28, 1947,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "and to Bureau teletype to Phoenix dated August 30, 1947.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "With reference to the above matter, I desire to point out that the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "letter of reference from San Francisco did not reach Phoenix until September",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "2, 1947.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "On August 29, 1947, a Mr. [REDACTED] called at the Phoenix",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "office and exhibited credentials reflecting that he is a representative of A-2,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "Fourth Air Force, Hamilton Field, California. He also exhibited orders emanating",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "from the office of Colonel [REDACTED] A-2, Fourth Air Force, Hamilton Field,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "California, instructing him to proceed to Phoenix immediately and contact the FBI b7c",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "office, at which time a Special Agent of the Federal Bureau of Investigation would",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "be designated to accompany him to interview [REDACTED] who had previously",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "reported the photographing of a flying disc. The orders further indicated that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "the San Francisco office of the FBI was transmitting further information re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "lating to Mr. [REDACTED] mission.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "ASAC [REDACTED] telephonically communicated with SAC HARRY KIMBALL",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "of the San Francisco office and Mr. KIMBALL verified the above information and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "stated that a letter had been directed to the Phoenix office suggesting that the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "Phoenix office assist any representative who called from A-2 in the interrogation b7c",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "of RHODES. SAC KIMBALL stated that in connection with flying discs, he had main-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "tained close contact with Colonel [REDACTED] and that close cooperation existed.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "He further advised that many reports of flying discs had been received at San",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "Francisco and that a full discussion concerning the results of inquiries had",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "been held with Colonel [REDACTED].",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "DEFERRED RECORDING",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "In connection with flying disc investigations, Mr. [REDACTED] advised",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "he had maintained close touch with the Bureau and had apparently handled these b7c",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "matters in accordance with Bureau policy.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "In view of the above, Special Agent [REDACTED] of the Phoenix",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "office was permitted to work with Mr. [REDACTED] in the interview of [REDACTED]. b7c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
